01:27:13,984 --> 01:27:15,360
Ada apa, Pollyanna?

687
01:27:15,944 --> 01:27:17,905
Kau tersesat dalam
perjalanan ke klub janapada?

688
01:27:27,998 --> 01:27:29,541
